item.title: MIGA
item.description: Make Internet Great Again! Parable of Two Webs Once upon a time in a digital land, there were two World Wide Webs, each unique and reflecting the lives of those who wandered through them. In the first web, there lived a person named Alex. Alex’s web was a vibrant and colourful place, filled with the wonders of knowledge and creativity. This web was a mirror of Alex’s life – organized, curious, and always seeking to learn.
